room_title: Escape room " Matter of the Mad Hatter" by The Clue Room in Denver
room_description: Thereâ€™s a Jabberwocky in town, and the Mad Hatter has lost his hat! He has not been seen since its disappearance, and the good people of Wonderland are in a panic. They are looking for a group of heroes to step up and help restore the Hatter to his former glory by finding his hat, as well as the legendary Vorpal sword, so that he may have a chance of defeating the evil beast. With the Jabberwocky an hour away, can you follow the trail of clues the Hatter has left for you to find these two items and save Wonderland?
